        <obo:IAO_0000115>A convex 3-D shape quality inhering in a bearer by virtue of the bearer&apos;s having a quadric surface in three dimensions obtained by rotating an ellipse about one of its principal axes. Includes spheres and oblate/prolate spheroids.</obo:IAO_0000115>
