        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PATO_0000052"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>A shape that inheres in a 2 dimensional entity, such as a cross section or projection of a 3 dimensional entity.</obo:IAO_0000115>
